Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.01,0:23:03.48,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}狂風巨浪 風起雲湧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.85,0:23:07.06,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(0,355)}這殘酷世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:10.94,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}你用最強的光
